description.zh: Black Forest Labs开发的快速图像生成模型，专注于速度和效率，生成时间短但质量稍低于pro版本。
description.en: Fast image generation model by Black Forest Labs, focused on speed and efficiency with shorter generation times but slightly lower quality than pro version.

description.zh: Black Forest Labs最新专业级图像生成模型，相比前代版本速度提升6倍，支持2K分辨率，图像质量显著提升。
description.en: Latest professional-grade image generation model by Black Forest Labs, 6x faster than previous versions, supports 2K resolution with significantly improved image quality.

description.zh: 开发版本的Flux模型，提供更多自定义选项和实验性功能，适合开发者和研究人员使用。
description.en: Development version of Flux model with more customization options and experimental features, suitable for developers and researchers.

description.zh: PrunaAI开发的快速图像生成模型，经过优化以提供成本效益的图像生成服务，平衡速度和质量。
description.en: Fast image generation model by PrunaAI, optimized for cost-effective image generation services, balancing speed and quality.

description.zh: Ideogram AI的快速版本，特别擅长在图像中渲染文本，支持中文字符和复杂排版，创意设计效果出色。
description.en: Fast version of Ideogram AI, excels at rendering text in images, supports Chinese characters and complex typography, excellent for creative designs.

description.zh: 专门生成SVG矢量图形的AI模型，适合创建高质量的标志、图标和可缩放图形，支持多种设计风格。
description.en: AI model specialized in generating SVG vector graphics, perfect for creating high-quality logos, icons, and scalable graphics with various design styles.

description.zh: 字节跳动开发的双语图像生成模型，原生支持2K分辨率输出，3秒快速生成，对中文prompt支持优秀，文字渲染准确。
description.en: Bilingual image generation model by ByteDance, natively supports 2K resolution output, 3-second generation, excellent Chinese prompt support with accurate text rendering.

description.zh: 基于Stable Diffusion的开源Midjourney风格图像生成模型，提供艺术化的图像生成效果，适合创意和艺术创作。
description.en: Open-source Midjourney-style image generation model based on Stable Diffusion, provides artistic image generation effects, suitable for creative and artistic creation.

description.zh: MiniMax开发的快速语音合成模型，支持中英双语，具有出色的情感表达和音色控制能力，生成速度快。
description.en: Fast speech synthesis model by MiniMax, supports Chinese and English bilingual, excellent emotional expression and voice control capabilities with fast generation speed.

description.zh: MiniMax的高清语音合成模型，支持中英双语，音质更佳，支持多种音色和情感表达，适合专业语音制作。
description.en: High-definition speech synthesis model by MiniMax, supports Chinese and English bilingual, superior audio quality, multiple voice tones and emotional expressions, suitable for professional voice production.

description.zh: 开源的8200万参数语音合成模型，支持多语言包括日语，轻量级设计，适合资源受限环境。
description.en: Open-source 82-million parameter speech synthesis model, supports multiple languages including Japanese, lightweight design suitable for resource-constrained environments.

description.zh: 基于ACE架构的音频生成模型，专注于音频效果处理和声音变换，适合音频后期制作和特效生成。
description.en: Audio generation model based on ACE architecture, focused on audio effects processing and sound transformation, suitable for audio post-production and effects generation.

description.zh: 基于潜在扩散模型的音频生成系统，能够根据文本描述生成高质量的音频内容，支持多种音频类型。
description.en: Audio generation system based on latent diffusion models, capable of generating high-quality audio content from text descriptions, supports various audio types.

description.zh: MiniMax开发的音乐生成模型，支持中英双语prompt，能够生成多种风格的音乐作品，具有良好的旋律连贯性。
description.en: Music generation model by MiniMax, supports Chinese and English bilingual prompts, capable of generating various styles of music with good melodic coherence.

description.zh: 基于Stable Audio的开源音频生成模型，提供稳定的音频生成能力，支持多种音频格式和风格。
description.en: Open-source audio generation model based on Stable Audio, provides stable audio generation capabilities, supports various audio formats and styles.

description.zh: Meta开发的音乐生成模型，基于Transformer架构，能够生成高质量的音乐片段，支持多种音乐风格和乐器。
description.en: Music generation model by Meta, based on Transformer architecture, capable of generating high-quality music segments, supports various music styles and instruments.

description.zh: 经过200个epoch训练的音乐生成模型，专注于生成具有特定风格的音乐片段，适合背景音乐制作。
description.en: Music generation model trained for 200 epochs, focused on generating music segments with specific styles, suitable for background music production.

description.zh: MiniMax海螺视频生成第二代模型，支持中文prompt，能够生成高清电影级视频，具有出色的动态表现和视觉美学。
description.en: MiniMax Hailuo second-generation video generation model, supports Chinese prompts, generates high-definition cinematic videos with excellent dynamics and visual aesthetics.

description.zh: 快手可灵AI大师版，支持中文prompt，在语义理解和动作控制方面表现卓越，能生成1080p高质量视频，支持复杂的镜头运动。
description.en: Kuaishou Kling AI Master version, supports Chinese prompts, excellent performance in semantic understanding and motion control, generates 1080p high-quality videos with complex camera movements.

description.zh: Google Veo 3的快速版本，专注于提供更快的视频生成速度，同时保持良好的视频质量和一致性。
description.en: Fast version of Google Veo 3, focused on providing faster video generation speed while maintaining good video quality and consistency.
